e:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Looka is best suited for startups, entrepreneurs, small businesses, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Visme, meanwhile, shines for marketers, educators, business professionals, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2016, Looka describes itself as \"AI-powered logo maker and brand identity design platform.\" Visme, established in 2013, positions itself as \"Design platform for creating presentations, infographics, and visual content.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
f:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Visme** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to more features (8 vs 5), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Looka is a poor choice — far from it. Looka excels in its own right, particularly for startups and entrepreneurs.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value excellent for data visualization, go with Visme. If quick ai-generated logo options matters more to you, Looka is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
